title: Allimy Womens Drawstring High Waist Wide Leg Jeans Straight Leg Washed Denim Jeans Pants
description: The Straight Wide Leg Jeans features a '90s high rise, five classic pockets, and comes in a medium stretch fit. We love the classic washed details that give it a casual look and feel.

The Jean is cut in a lightweight denim and designed with a wide leg, a drawstring waist, and a full length inseam. Can easily go from beach to dinner with the addition of some jewelry and a strappy heel.
The perfect tailored touch to your denim drawer, these jeans from High Waist Wide Leg Jeans Straight Leg Washed Denim Jeans will be your go-to all season long.
